# Escalation Runbook

Risk tier: **{{risk_tier}}**

## Escalation Triggers

- Any security vulnerability (CVSS ≥ 7.0) → immediate escalation
- Data breach or unauthorized access → P0 incident
- Compliance violation → legal team notification within 1 hour

